        <h4 class="section-title">閱讀活動</h4>
        <p>
            We keep track of your reading activity to provide you with information such as reading stats, and improve personalized book recommendations. If you would like to turn it off on your eReader you may do so via Settings &gt;Energy saving and privacy &gt; Uncheck – Help improve our App.
        </p>


